{"word":"G3806 - πάθος - páthos - path'-os - Affection","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάθος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">páthos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">path'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Affection</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"இச்சை, துர்இச்சை - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"emotion, passion; passionate desire"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the alternate of <a href=\"#/G3958 - πάσχω - páschō - pas'-kho/3958\">G3958</a>; properly <i>suffering</i> (&ldquo;pathos&rdquo;), that is, (subjectively) a <i>passion</i> (especially <i>concupiscence</i>): - (inordinate) affection, lust.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2552/2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553/2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356/3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663/3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804/3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805/3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806/3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958/3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236/4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310/4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777/4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834/4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835/4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>"}]}